#: .\manim\main.py:50
msgid ""
"This circle is drawn as I speak. The scene will wait for this sentence to "
"finish before proceeding."
msgstr "这个圆圈在我说话时绘制完成。场景将等待这句话结束才继续。"

#: .\manim\main.py:57
msgid ""
"Let's shift the circle to the left 2 units... This animation takes as long "
"as this text to be read."
msgstr "现在将圆圈向左移动2个单位...这个动画的持续时间等同于阅读此文本所需的时间。"

#: .\manim\main.py:70
msgid ""
"You can <bookmark mark='A'/>trigger animations <bookmark mark='B'/>at any "
"word in the middle of a sentence by adding <bookmark mark='C'/>bookmarks to "
"your text."
msgstr "你可以在句子中的任意<bookmark mark='A'/>单词处添加<bookmark mark='B'/>书签<bookmark mark='C'/>来触发动画。"

#: .\manim\main.py:96
msgid ""
"Here is another example for more fine-tuned bookmarking. Super<bookmark "
"mark='A'/>cali<bookmark mark='B'/>fragilistic<bookmark mark='C'/"
">expiali<bookmark mark='D'/>docious."
msgstr "下面是另一个<bookmark mark='A'/>更精细<bookmark mark='B'/>的书签示例<bookmark mark='C'/>。 超级<bookmark mark='D'/>无敌妙不可言。"

#: .\manim\main.py:125
msgid ""
"Now let's talk about subtitles. Subtitles are automatically generated as a "
"\".srt\" file next to the video output. By default, the subtitle is the same "
"as the text, however you can modify this behavior by specifying the "
"subcaption property."
msgstr "现在谈谈字幕。字幕会自动生成与视频输出并列的\".srt\"文件。默认情况下字幕内容与文本相同，但可通过指定subcaption属性修改此行为。"

#: .\manim\main.py:128
msgid ""
"This is a custom subcaption that lasts the duration of this scene. You can "
"say facts like Yotsuba is the best Quintuplet."
msgstr "这是持续整个场景的自定义字幕。 例如可添加\"四叶草才是最棒的五胞胎\"这类事实说明。"

#: .\manim\main.py:135
msgid ""
"Why would this be helpful? Many times, we want to insert LaTeX into the "
"subcaptions, however the text-to-speech isn't able to pronounce it "
"correctly. As an example, here's the L2 norm of a vector and Mass-energy "
"Equivalence."
msgstr "为何这样做有帮助？我们常需在字幕中插入LaTeX公式，但文本转语音功能无法正确发音。例如：此处为向量的L2范数及质量能量等效原理。"

#: .\manim\main.py:138
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Why would this be helpful? Many times, we want to insert LaTeX into the "
"subcaptions, however the text-to-speech isn't able to pronounce it "
"correctly. As an example, here's $\\left\\lVert{x}\\right\\rVert_2$ and $e = "
"mc^2$"
msgstr "为何这样做有帮助？ 我们常需在字幕中插入LaTeX公式，但文本转语音系统无法正确发音。例如：此处为$\\left\\lVert{x}\\right\\rVert_2$  该$e = mc^2$"

#: .\manim\main.py:145
msgid ""
"This also allows us to add SSML-like customizations to the voiceover, like "
"\"insert emotion\" into the voices ———————— or add \"pauses\"....... without "
"affecting the subcaption. This works on ElevenLabs... but not GTTS."
msgstr "功能还支持为旁白添加SSML类自定义效果，如在语音中插入\"情感表达\"——————或添加\"停顿\"....... 而不会影响字幕内容。此功能在ElevenLabs上有效...但在GTTS上"

#: .\manim\main.py:148
msgid ""
"This also allows us to add SSML-like customizations to the voiceover, like "
"insert emotion into the voices, or add pauses... without affecting the "
"subcaption. This works on ElevenLabs but not GTTS."
msgstr "无效。"